<div id="addendums" class="addendums"><div class="story-addendum theme-correction"><strong>Correction: November 15, 2014</strong> <br>An earlier version of this post misstated the year of Gen. Philip H. Sheridan's campaign in the Shenandoah Valley. It was in 1864, of course, not 1964.</div></div><footer class="story-footer">
